      <title>美联储理事表示不急于降息后油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-falls-after-us-fed-governor-says-no-rush-cut-interest-rates-2024-02-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储官员表示降息应至少再推迟两个月后，周五油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-falls-after-us-fed-governor-says-no-rush-cut-interest-rates-2024-02-23/</guid>
