    <item>
      <title>美联储沃勒认为“不急于”降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-waller-sees-no-rush-cut-interest-rates-2024-02-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事克里斯托弗·沃勒(Christopher Waller)周四表示，美联储政策制定者应将降息至少再推迟几个月，看看近期通胀上升是否预示着物价稳定进程陷入停滞，还是只是路上的一个坎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-waller-sees-no-rush-cut-interest-rates-2024-02-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 00:37:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管需求放缓，龙舌兰酒巨头 Becle 利润仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tequila-giant-becle-posts-4th-quarter-profit-rise-2024-02-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的龙舌兰酒生产商墨西哥酿酒商 Becle 周四公布，尽管主要市场销量下滑，但 2023 年最后三个月的净利润较上年同期增长 41%，高于市场预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tequila-giant-becle-posts-4th-quarter-profit-rise-2024-02-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 00:13:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡电信第三季度利润持平，本地业绩疲软抵消了 Optus 的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/singtel-posts-flat-net-profit-third-quarter-2024-02-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡电信（SingTel）周五表示，其第三季度基本净利润与去年持平，因为本地业务疲软抵消了其信息技术和澳大利亚电信部门的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/singtel-posts-flat-net-profit-third-quarter-2024-02-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 00:10:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路透调查显示，未来几个月全球股市将上涨，而非烟花爆竹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/poll-global-stocks-set-gains-not-fireworks-months-ahead-2024-02-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社对股票策略师的一项调查显示，考虑到去年出人意料的大幅上涨，全球股市近期的涨势仅剩一点点。对于未来三个月是否会出现调整，股票策略师的意见不一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/poll-global-stocks-set-gains-not-fireworks-months-ahead-2024-02-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 00:08:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
